{"tid":2180889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿南蒙古學校汉語授課　家長欲接走子女與公安衝突","createTime":"2020-08-30T08:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T15:43:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"39d8e422204fbf0506eac58acab36a96e2eea4c5","tid":2180889,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:03:20.000Z","msg":"內蒙古近日要求所有學校在新學期使用漢語取代蒙古語教學（蒙古語課除外），引發當地人抗議，有家長更前往學校接走子女以示不滿，卻傳出遭警察鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n據總部設在美國紐約的關注內蒙古人權組織上周六（29日）表示，政府的決定引發當地普遍不滿，有教師也參加罷課，抗議政府進行文化滅絕，不少學生穿上蒙古傳統服裝上街抗議。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，在不同學校外，有學生家長要求接走子女，卻遭警察攔阻。有家長突破警察防線，並接走子女；但亦有人被警察毆打並帶走。消息稱，事件中有數百人被當局拘留或軟禁在家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200830/photo/bkn-20200830151256726-0830_00952_001_01p.jpg?20200830153541\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200830151256726-0830_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20200830153541&h=aa96e921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網傳畫面顯示公安與市民對峙<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200830/bkn-20200830151256726-0830_00952_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6ad58b41d067cdac8bdb425b17b0fe0a20bacd3f","tid":2180889,"uid":252142,"like":4,"dislike":25,"score":-21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5809d9937b88f206cefd2291265fb030f513f1d6","tid":2180889,"uid":313839,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"6ad58b41d067cdac8bdb425b17b0fe0a20bacd3f","tid":2180889,"uid":252142,"like":4,"dislike":25,"score":-21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:09:32.000Z","msg":"賤種五毛"},{"pid":"69cd40c85650bb72a1f5690b24b5d8ca6ccb6f9d","tid":2180889,"uid":348747,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"2025年香港都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ae345b65a10324026362b75f7411f3b1c5edca","tid":2180889,"uid":524